bio: The Woopax are not only a multimedia project:  Woopax is a way of life!  Woo means to court or to endeavour towards  Pax comes from Latin and means peace.  Two artists, each successful in his own profession  as a designer, as a musician and writer  have, despite a combined professional experience of 60 years, decided to keep alive the child within themselves. Together they have developed a lifestyle and are trying  both together and as individuals  to live the Woopax lifestyle and reinvent it every day.  York Penno & Tom Haugh woopax company
